OL,3,CGovernment spending #4m a year on
OL,4,C'unusable' prison with no inmates
OL,6,FThe Government is spending #4 million
OL,7,Fa year on the upkeep of an "unusable"
OL,8,Fprison in Devon which currently holds
OL,9,Fno inmates, MPs have revealed.
OL,11,FHMP Dartmoor was shut down in August
OL,12,F2024 after abnormal levels of
OL,13,Fradioactive radon gas had been
OL,14,Fdetected at the jail in Princetown.
OL,16,FMore than 600 inmates had to be
OL,17,Frelocated from the category C
OL,18,Ffacility, adding to the national
OL,19,Fcrisis around the shortage of prison
OL,20,Fplaces.
