OL,3,CGovernment spending #4m a year on
OL,4,C'unusable' prison with no inmates
OL,6,F"HMPPS's failure to negotiate a good
OL,7,Fdeal when it renewed the lease on HMP
OL,8,FDartmoor in March 2022 means it is now
OL,9,Fspending #4 million of taxpayers'
OL,10,Fmoney a year on rent, rates and
OL,11,Fsecurity for a prison it cannot use,"
OL,12,Fa report from the House of Commons
OL,13,FPublic Accounts Committee revealed on
OL,14,FWednesday.
OL,16,F"This arrangement will continue until
OL,17,Feither the prison can be reoccupied or
OL,18,Fit can end the lease in 2033."
