OL,3,CGovernment spending #4m a year on
OL,4,C'unusable' prison with no inmates
OL,6,FIt urged justice officials to "set out
OL,7,Fwhat it has learned from the failures
OL,8,Fof its decision making and contract
OL,9,Fmanagement of the HMP Dartmoor lease
OL,10,Fnegotiations, and how it will ensure
OL,11,Fthat any future contracts deliver
OL,12,Fvalue for money".
OL,14,FThe MPs, led by committee chairman Sir
OL,15,FGeoffrey Clifton-Brown, said the MoJ
OL,16,Fhad set out its ambition to bring HMP
OL,17,FDartmoor back into use, but found "no
OL,18,Fclear plans for how and when they will
OL,19,Fdo this".
OL,26,@nD@_OUtD@PO]yD@cOU{D@HO]
