OL,4,C'unusable' prison with no inmates
OL,6,FThe Health and Safety Executive is
OL,7,Fcurrently investigating the radon
OL,8,Flevels, and a decision on reopening
OL,9,Fthe jail must wait until after the
OL,10,Fresults have been delivered.
OL,12,FIt has also been revealed that #1.2
OL,13,Fmillion has been spent so far by the
OL,14,FMoJ on radon mitigation works, but
OL,15,Fthat effort has been halted until the
OL,16,Ffindings of the HSE investigation are
OL,17,Fknown.
