OL,3,CGovernment spending #4m a year on
OL,4,C'unusable' prison with no inmates
OL,6,FIn September last year, legal action
OL,7,Fwas launched against the prison
OL,8,Fservice by a collection of staff,
OL,9,Finmates, and former prisoners at HMP
OL,10,FDartmoor, alleging they were wrongly
OL,11,Fexposed to high levels of radon.
OL,13,FThe odourless and colourless gas forms
OL,14,Ffrom decaying uranium, and can lead to
OL,15,Fillnesses including lung cancer.
OL,17,FThe Ministry of Justice has been
OL,18,Fcontacted for comment.
